CommentBody:
Thank you for your time today.
We created a new job and SQL ViewCreation in today's meeting.
All StealthAUDIT Tables

For the Input Source: I joined the SA_ADInventory_UsersView and SA_ADInventory_GroupMembersView

Join Columns: Table1=PrincipalId and Table2=MemberPrincipalId and the Join Type=INNER

Columns: For SA_ADInventory_GroupMembersView, I select "GroupNTAccount
For SA_ADInventory_UsersView, I select SamAccountName and ACCOUNTDISABLE

Filter: I added this filter: [SourceTable1.ACCOUNTDISABLE] = True

Next…Next…Finish and execute the analysis

For some reason, the table did not show all domains.
We reviewed the report filter and readjusted it so that it shows all the admins' groups. We also changed the result from PDF to CSV.
